    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_nVq5LJCpkrSdbcau",
      "label": "Title",
      "default": "<h3>FALL ASLEEP FASTER,</h3><h3>SLEEP DEEPER</h3>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_xjcw9LS5wNYGxm7W",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>Tossing and turning? Not anymore.</p><p>BKM Tranquil combines calming magnesium and plant-based nutrients to help you fall asleep faster and stay deeply asleep — so you wake up refreshed, not groggy.</p>"
