      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_Y4PVwJXc2CJph4x4",
      "label": "Title",
      "default": "<h3>DEVELOPED WITH LI KARLSÉN, OUR CO-FOUNDER AND EXPERT IN RECOVERY</h3>"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "text_EUnvgM02rarQj8Uy",
      "label": "Text",
      "default": "<p>This formula was created together with our co-founder Li Karlsén, world record holder and expert in recovery, drawing on insights from leading sleep scientists and nutritionists. Every ingredient is carefully chosen to support deep, restorative sleep and overnight recovery.</p>"
